nodes.text: Garbage Masher was an online game found on StarWars.com. In the game, the player has to save Luke Skywalker, Han Solo, Leia Organa and Chewbacca from the Death Star's Garbage compactor by correctly answering questions throughout four levels. The game is no longer available on the site.
